title: Topaz Plug-ins Bundle 03.06.2016 for Mac OSX - CORE
description:
The Topaz Photography Collection

System requirements

- OSX 10.8+ (Topaz is NOT compatible with PowerPC processors - like G4 or G5.)
- 4 GB RAM minimum - preferably more
- 64bit CPU

Topaz Plug-ins Bundle for Adobe Photoshop helps amateur and professional photographers accomplish the most common creative and corrective post processing tasks.
With 14 powerful and easy-to-use programs, users can quickly enhance their digital images with flexible adjustments that are easy to apply and customize - and often in just 1-click!

Features

- Instantly convert your photos into an exciting art
- Control of the artistic process with an infinitely configurable options
- Use simple, fast and easy to master sliders
- Maximizing productivity through the use of a number of built-in presets
- Save your settings in your own presets
- Take advantage of multiple processors for faster processing
- Use Photoshop smart filter for convenient and non-destructive editing

Includes

- Topaz Adjust 5.1.0
- Topaz ReStyle 1.0.0
- Topaz Clarity 1.0.0
- Topaz ReMask 5.0.0
- Topaz B&W Effects 2.1.0
- Topaz Detail 3.2.0
- Topaz Simplify 4.1.1
- Topaz Lens Effects 1.2.0
- Topaz Star Effects 1.1.0
- Topaz Clean 3.1.0
- Topaz DeNoise 6.0.1
- Topaz InFocus 1.0.0
- Topaz DeJPEG 4.0.2
- Topaz photoFXlab 1.2.10
